<p>I have a db like this</p>  <p>id | date | time from | time to</p>  <p>1 | 2015-09-19 | 20:00 | 04:00</p>  <p>2 | 2015-09-19 | 10:00 | 23:00</p>  <p>3 | 2015-09-19 | 22:00 | 10:00</p>  <p>4 | 2015-09-20 | 10:00 | 16:00</p>  <p>For each row, I need hour between 22:00 and 06:00</p>  <p>Then first row have 6, second row have 1, third row have 8, fourth row have nothing.</p>